      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De zelo (in De gratiosis)</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e104">Gregorius, <title>super Ezechielem</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e112">Nullum omnipotenti Deo tale est sacrificium,
              quale est zelus animarum.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e119">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e127">Si nulla ira ex virtute surgeret, divinae
              animadversionis impetum Phinees per gladium non placasset.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e132">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e142" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e134">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e142">Aliquando necesse est ut pravis mentibus, quae
              humana praedicatione corrigi nequeunt, divina flagella optari benigne debeant.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e147">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e157" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e149">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e157">Si sic proximos ut nos amare praecipimur, restat
              ut sic eorum erratibus sicut nostris vitiis irascamur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e163">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e173" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e165">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e173">Erga errata proximorum sic mansuetudo zelum
              temperet, quatenus a justitiae studio non enervet.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e178">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e188" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e180">Augustinus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e188">Quid hic magis persequitur vitam bonorum, quam
              vita iniquorum; non cum cogit imitari quod displicet, sed cum cogit dolere quod videt?
              Quoniam coram pio vivens impie, etsi non obligat consentientem, cruciat
              sentientem.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e193">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e203" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e195">Bernardus, <title>super Cantica</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e203">Zelum tuum inflammet charitas, informet
              scientia, firmet constantia: sit fervidus, sit circumspectus, sit invictus, nec
              teporem habeat, nec discretione careat, nec timidus sit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e208">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e218" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e210">Bernardus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e218">Habeat charitas zelum; sed adhibeat pro tempore
              modum: severitas nunquam remissa; intermissa tamen plus proficit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e223">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e233" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e225">Bernardus, in <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e233">Hoc vera et casta contemplatio habet, ut mentem
              quanto divino igne vehementer succenderit, tanto interdum repleat zelo, et desiderio
              acquirendi Deo qui eum similiter diligant, ut otium contemplationis pro studio
              praedicationis libentissime intermittat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e238">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e245" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e240">Glossa</ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e245">Ira justa est, qua irascitur quis suis et
              alienis peccatis, videns homines confitentes Deum ore, et negantes moribus;
              renuntiantes saeculo verbis, et non factis; et videns fratres fratribus detrahentes,
              osculum dantes, et fidem non servantes.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-d1e251">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e258" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Rd1e253">Glossa</ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e45830-Qd1e258">Bonus zelus est fervor animi, quo mens, abjecto
              humano timore, pro defensione veritatis accenditur, et eo magis commendabilis, quo
              quaelibet prava, quae viderit, corrigere satagit; si nequit, tolerat et gemit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
